The video shows the terrifying moments an Uber driver was robbed and nearly killed.
The violent robbery happened around 12:45 a.m. on Valentine’s Day in Atascocita. The gunmen blocked the female driver’s car at the intersection of Timber Forest and Eagle Springs. Pointing a gun at her head, they demand her money and phone and repeatedly threaten to kill her.
“I’m going to shoot you. Give me your (expletive) money,” yelled a robber. The robbers grab a few things and it appears they leave. Clutching her dog, the terror takes over.The gunmen had circled back and fired three shots at her car. One hit inches from her head. Released by Harris County Sheriff’s Office released